Description:
    Creates a new bot and adds it to the telegram_bot_rails_bots table. It also creates the template for the responder

Example:
    rails generate bot Thing ABCDEF1234

    This will create:
        - an entry in the 'telegram_bot_rails_bots' table that will be used for bot lookup
        - a responder called 'things_responder.rb' located in 'app/responders'
